; $VER: Network-Startup 1.0 (AmiTCP_NG)
;
; Bring up every network interface configured under DEVS:NetInterfaces/. Each
; file there describes one interface (see the examples in SYS:Storage/NetInterfaces).
; This runs from S:User-Startup so the network is up by the time Workbench opens.
;
; The pattern ~(#?.info) matches every file EXCEPT Workbench .info icons.
FailAt 30
AddNetInterface DEVS:NetInterfaces/~(#?.info)
